{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about","content_id":"c63160be-9dec-4b5d-bfdb-61a56fd223b6","description":"We scrutinise new free trade agreements (FTAs) once they are signed. We are independent of the Department for Business and Trade (DBT) and DBT ministers play no part in the TAC’s advice on FTAs.  However, we are supported by a small Secretariat, which is based in DBT.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>The Trade and Agriculture Commission (<abbr title=\"Trade and Agriculture Commission\">TAC</abbr>) is an independent expert committee comprising specialists in:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>UK animal and plant health standards</li>\n  <li>UK animal welfare standards</li>\n  <li>UK environmental standards as they relate to agricultural products</li>\n  <li>International trade law and policy</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We have evolved from the original <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/trade-and-agriculture-commission-tac\">Trade and Agriculture Commission</a>, which was set up in July 2020 as an independent, time-limited body to advise on specific questions to inform the UK’s trade and agriculture policy.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-we-do\">What we do</h2>\n\n<p>Our role is to scrutinise new <abbr title=\"free trade agreements\">FTAs</abbr> once they are signed, to inform Parliament’s understanding of whether measures within <abbr title=\"free trade agreements\">FTAs</abbr> are consistent with the maintenance of UK levels of statutory protection in relation to UK animal and plant health, animal welfare, and environmental standards.</p>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Trade and Agriculture Commission\">TAC</abbr> does not inform or comment on negotiations.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"reporting\">Reporting</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Trade and Agriculture Commission\">TAC</abbr>’s role was approved by Parliament during passage of the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/10/section/8/enacted\">Trade Act 2021</a> and <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2020/21/section/42\">Agriculture Act 2020</a>.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2022-11-07T11:03:44Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["3946ea8e-f4dc-4d8f-82ba-d24a83725c54","770e6cac-38ba-42dc-8e58-237278f9f4d7"],"name":"Access our information"}],"headers":[{"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are"},{"id":"what-we-do","level":2,"text":"What we do"},{"id":"reporting","level":2,"text":"Reporting"}],"organisation":"bc2ea18e-ff22-4698-9941-01d087ab544b","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2022-11-07T11:03:44+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about","content_id":"c63160be-9dec-4b5d-bfdb-61a56fd223b6","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-11-07T11:03:44Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about","withdrawn":false}],"corporate_information_pages":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about/membership","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about/membership","base_path":"/government/organisations/trade-and-agriculture-commission/about/membership","content_id":"3946ea8e-f4dc-4d8f-82ba-d24a83725c54","document_type":"membership","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-15T08:30:01Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Membership","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/gov